Title: Jobs in Meghalaya : Apply for teaching positions in Army Public School Shillong
Festivals: ['A-Film Teens Fest - International Online Children and Youth Film Festival', 'Jean Rouch International Film Festival', 'Poitiers Film Festival']
Narrative:
Applications are invited for various teaching positions in Army Public School Shillong.

Army Public School Shillong is inviting applications from eligible candidates for the posts of Post Graduate Teacher (PGT), Trained Graduate Teacher (TGT), Primary Teacher (PRT), Physical Education Teacher (PET) and School Counselor on adhoc/part-time basis.
